l=[]
for i in numerical:
    Count=len(df_teleco[i])
    Min=round(df_teleco[i].min(),2)
    Max=round(df_teleco[i].max(),2)
    Mean=round(df_teleco[i].mean(),2)
    sd=round(df_teleco[i].std(),2)
    Median=round(df_teleco[i].median(),2)
    P_25=round(np.percentile(df_teleco[i],25),2)
    P_50=round(np.percentile(df_teleco[i],50),2)
    P_75=round(np.percentile(df_teleco[i],75),2)
    
    coloums =['Count','Min','Max','Mean','sd','Median','P_25','P_50','P_75']
    values = [Count,Min,Max,Mean,sd,Median,P_25,P_50,P_75]
    l.append(values)
df_statistical = pd.DataFrame(l,index=numerical,columns=coloums)

In[175]:
q3=np.percentile(age_data,75)
q1=np.percentile(age_data,25)
IQR=q3-q1
upper_limit_age_data=q3+1.5*IQR
lower_limit_age_data=q1-1.5*IQR
con1=age_data > upper_limit_age_data
con2=age_data < lower_limit_age_data
con3 = con1 | con2
outlier_of_age_data = df_teleco[con3]
print("The outlier data of age feacture is :",len(outlier_of_age_data))
con4=age_data < upper_limit_age_data
con5=age_data > lower_limit_age_data
con6 = con4 & con5
Non_outlier_of_age_data = df_teleco[con6]
print("The Non outlier data of age feacture is :",len(Non_outlier_of_age_data))

The outlier data of age feacture is : 63
The Non outlier data of age feacture is : 1926

q3_weekly_max_night_mins = np.percentile(df_teleco['weekly_max_night_mins'], 75)
q1_weekly_max_night_mins = np.percentile(df_teleco['weekly_max_night_mins'], 25)
IQR_weekly_max_night_mins = q3_weekly_max_night_mins - q1_weekly_max_night_mins

    df_teleco['weekly_max_night_mins'],

lower_limit_videos_watched=q1_videos_watched-1.5*IQR_videos_watched
new_data_videos_watched=np.clip(df_telecom['videos_watched'],lower_limit_videos_watched,upper_limit_videos_watched)
